    Fast approximation of centrality . 
D. Eppstein and
 J. Wang .  arXiv:cs.DS/0009005 .  
 12th ACM-SIAM Symp. Discrete Algorithms, 
Washington, 2001, pp. 228–229 .   J. Graph Algorithms &amp; Applications  8 (1): 39–45, 2004 .
 
We use random sampling to quickly estimate, for each vertex in a graph,
the average  distance  to all other vertices.
  
