    A steady state model for graph power laws . 
D. Eppstein and
 J. Wang .  2nd Int.
Worksh. Web Dynamics , Honolulu, 2002.  arXiv:cs.DM/0204001 .
 
We propose a random graph model that (empirically) appears to have a
power law degree distribution.  Unlike previous models, our model is
based on a Markov process rather than incremental growth.  We compare
our model with others in its ability to predict web graph clustering
behavior.
  
